## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the role of traditional news media. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the rapidly evolving media landscape means that the role of traditional media is subject to change, and newer studies may provide updated insights.